item.title: Now
item.description: August 2022 ∘ Learning C with "Learning C for Pebble". ∘ Working on an accessible version of my iPod theme for people with eyesight problems. ∘ Expanding the sight a little more. ∘ Start looking for a new home server on Mastodon. What’s Playing? ∘ Listening to Snail Mail a bunch. ∘ Currently reading Nausicaä of the Valley of the Wind. ∙ now 2022
